  "title": "今日开源（2026-2-9）：美团 LongCat-Flash-Lite 开源，256k 长上下文+MoE 高效推理，嵌入优化超越等效基线",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501588&idx=1&sn=9aade4d280c20d77f9840b0c2de6e9ca",
  "date": "2026-02-09 10:31:00",
