  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：LongCat-Flash-Lite</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"522\" data-imgfileid=\"100017932\" data-ratio=\"0.32592592592592595\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c5fda74&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZyZdVVuUcYfYT90gfasfbkib3V58iaBaYbtHcCdELly3lOZ1X4yCFbRXCt4NYuZBMzmgcr7tibzgt4Yv0c4GOyJfIviadkxFCvFBE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LongCat-Flash-Lite是一个具有68.5B参数的Mixture-of-Experts (MoE)模型，支持256k上下文长度。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">YaRN方法</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">N-gram嵌入表</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的集成，提升了模型性能和推理速度。尽管分配了超过30B参数用于嵌入，LongCat-Flash-Lite不仅优于参数等效的MoE基线，还在Agent和编码领域表现出色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/longcat-flash-lite\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/longcat-flash-lite</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Motus</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1119\" data-imgfileid=\"100017934\" data-ratio=\"0.6990740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f779d84&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFay8wDrnvoVecWYohuzXPdTnV85JuicJ9TZ4DzPk4ibkgUIOGfX2bicISc13dGKqoibZBC1jy0MC53TLk6vnibRZBjGPZoZ9LkW31Zk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Motus是一个统一的潜在动作世界模型，利用现有的预训练模型和丰富的可共享运动信息。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它引入了一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">混合变压器（Mixture-of-Transformers, MoT）架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，整合了理解、动作和视频生成三个专家模块，并采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">UniDiffuser风格</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的调度器，实现了在不同建模模式之间的灵活切换。Motus通过光流学习潜在动作，采用三阶段训练流程和六层数据金字塔，从而提取像素级别的“增量动作”，并实现大规模动作预训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/motus\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/motus</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：IntelliFold</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"624\" data-imgfileid=\"100017933\" data-ratio=\"0.38981481481481484\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b3b15a35&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFasZKRZeFicKjwiamqYICxwpkxIDRgXoSWbhZFsNJuFnfFbibdU5HzIVohicQ86hibuk5JD2Qetg2WFKialibXia9oLfyQnBeS6FerM7JA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★IntelliFold是一个用于通用和专业生物分子结构预测的可控基础模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目的最新版本IntelliFold 2在架构上进行了重大更新，是首批在Foldbench上超越AlphaFold3的开源模型之一。IntelliFold提供了一个直观的Web界面，用户可以直接在浏览器中</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">提交序列并可视化结果</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，适合需要高精度和便捷性的生物分子结构预测任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/intellifold\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/intellifold</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：UI-TARS Desktop</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"444\" data-imgfileid=\"100017931\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a9510979&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFaKkhkiaao5ic2ichlbHdnz429bGhHiclMUZJcDQuyXNicwuYou5ej3CIH0GrB1mFkBa03togL6dNLVTroC7AZNWcxeZfeXxpgibiblHI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UI-TARS Desktop是一个基于UI-TARS模型的桌面应用程序，提供本地和远程计算机以及浏览器操作的原生GUI Agent。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目旨在通过尖端的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态大语言模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">（LLM）和与</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">各种现实世界工具</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的无缝集成，提供更接近人类任务完成的工作流程。UI-TARS Desktop提供了一种新的智能和便捷的计算机使用体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ui-tars-desktop\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ui-tars-desktop</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：DreamZero</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1249\" data-imgfileid=\"100017935\" data-ratio=\"0.7805555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f95c777f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFYOnYibN7CO9icibZfpctbRzMQNdGlMicwLutfKTHR6yy6icvy0P9DD5MLdhMhibMU6zFPOJDQuuEKH1JIjby20GA3jZcia3EDEJOXjdM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DreamZero是一个世界动作模型，能够同时预测动作和视频，在未见任务上实现强大的零样本性能。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了预训练的DreamZero模型检查点，并通过WebSocket服务器进行分布式推理。项目支持DROID模拟评估和RoboArena集成，能够生成和保存视频。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dreamzero\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/dreamzero</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：ProjDevBench</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"1086\" data-imgfileid=\"100017936\" data-ratio=\"0.6787037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=20e914c1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFaDb6UtpAnnSWFlJxmHicibArxIe1xl219SicEUibDr6fEcNicY4dibUpuSibOgsDcmLyLxjl11nsdL7o2sonzqP9ECVo8GuZMonCYria0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ProjDevBench是一个用于评估AI编码Agent在端到端项目开发任务中的表现的基准平台。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与现有的专注于问题级别错误修复的基准不同，ProjDevBench评估Agent从高层次规范构建完整、可执行软件库的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/projdevbench\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/projdevbench</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 2 月初发布的多个前沿开源 AI 项目，重点介绍了美团 LongCat-Flash-Lite 长上下文模型及其他在世界模型、生物分子预测和 AI 编码评测领域的突破。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 2 月初发布的多个前沿开源 AI 项目，重点介绍了美团 LongCat-Flash-Lite 长上下文模型及其他在世界模型、生物分子预测和 AI 编码评测领域的突破。",
  "summary": "文章精选并简要介绍了六项最新的开源 AI 技术成果。核心项目包括美团开发的 LongCat-Flash-Lite，这是一个 68.5B 参数的 MoE 模型，支持 256k 长上下文并针对嵌入表进行了推理优化；Motus 潜在动作世界模型，采用混合变压器架构实现像素级动作提取；IntelliFold 2 在生物分子结构预测上超越了 AlphaFold3；UI-TARS Desktop 提供了原生 GUI Agent 体验；DreamZero 实现了动作与视频的同步预测；以及 ProjDevBench 这一针对 AI 编码 Agent 的端到端项目开发基准平台。这些项目反映了 AI 在长文本处理、具身智能和科学计算领域的快速演进。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "美团 LongCat-Flash-Lite 通过 MoE 架构和嵌入优化提升了长文本处理能力。",
      "explanation": "该模型利用 YaRN 方法支持 256k 上下文，并通过 N-gram 嵌入表集成提升推理速度，在 Agent 和编码任务中表现优于同类基线模型。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Motus 和 DreamZero 展示了世界模型在动作预测与视频生成融合方面的最新进展。",
      "explanation": "这些模型通过混合变压器架构或分布式推理，实现了从像素级动作提取到零样本视频预测的跨越，为具身智能提供了更强的环境理解能力。"
